<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="234" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,222,679]" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,294,319]" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species was found in heavily vegetated river alluvia in species-rich assemblages of aquatic invertebrates including the following water bugs: 
<taxonomicName box="[727,879,331,354]" class="Insecta" family="Nepidae" genus="Nepa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cinerea">
<emphasis box="[727,879,331,354]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Nepa cinerea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[896,1149,331,355]" class="Insecta" family="Corixidae" genus="Hesperocorixa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="linnaei">
<emphasis box="[896,1149,331,355]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Hesperocorixa linnaei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[1166,1324,331,354]" class="Insecta" family="Corixidae" genus="Sigara" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="striata">
<emphasis box="[1166,1324,331,354]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Sigara striata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Corixidae" genus="Cymatia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coleoptrata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Cymatia coleoptrata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[304,540,366,390]" class="Insecta" family="Naucoridae" genus="Ilyocoris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cimicoides">
<emphasis box="[304,540,366,390]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Ilyocoris cimicoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[564,771,366,390]" class="Insecta" family="Notonectidae" genus="Notonecta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="glauca">
<emphasis box="[564,771,366,390]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Notonecta glauca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[796,998,366,390]" class="Insecta" family="Pleidae" genus="Plea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minutissima">
<emphasis box="[796,998,366,390]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Plea minutissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[1023,1290,366,390]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrometridae" genus="Hydrometra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gracilenta">
<emphasis box="[1023,1290,366,390]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Hydrometra gracilenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Veliidae" genus="Microvelia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="reticulata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="234">Microvelia reticulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[313,511,403,426]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Gerris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="234" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argentatus">
